                             'LineBloks' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'LineBloks' is @{" played " link play} on an 8 by 8 tile board, the idea is to
align 8 tiles of the same pattern in a row or column. When a row or
column is filled with the same type of tiles, those tiles are
removed from the board.

  As the game progress, in addition to the normal tiles, Bombs,
Unclickable tiles, Lightning tiles and Blocks are added on the
game board.

  Have fun!

